Package: opencog-matrix
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         libcogutil3 (>= 2.1.0),
         opencog-atomspace (>= 5.0.5)
Description: Sparse matrix and vector support for OpenCog AtomSpace
 The Matrix library provides sparse matrix and vector operations
 for the OpenCog AtomSpace hypergraph database. It enables efficient
 storage and manipulation of large-scale sparse data structures
 commonly used in machine learning and statistical analysis.
 .
 Key features:
  - Sparse matrix representation using AtomSpace
  - Vector operations and transformations
  - Matrix multiplication and decomposition
  - Integration with AtomSpace queries
  - Support for large-scale data processing
 .
 This package is part of the OpenCog AGI framework.
